    "_postman_id": "81349b65-f4bb-4ba8-95b2-f5309be3fadf",
    "name": "Auth",
    "description": "Overview\nThe Auth collection handles user registration and login to obtain the bearer token used by other collections.\n\nBase URL\nAll requests use {{BaseURL}}, e.g., {{BaseURL}}/auth/login\n\nAuthentication\nNo inherited auth is applied to this collection. Use these endpoints to obtain a token and store it in the Environment Variable environment variable token.\n\nRequest descriptions\n- REGISTER USER — Registers a new user account.\n- LOGIN USER — Authenticates a user and returns an access token.\n\nUsage with other collections\n- Ticket and Comment collections inherit bearer auth using {{token}}.\n\nRun in Postman\nUse the Run in Postman button to import this collection and select Environment Variable so variables like {{BaseURL}} are available.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "41718582",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/41718582-81349b65-f4bb-4ba8-95b2-f5309be3fadf?source=collection_link"
  },
